{# Who we are #}
<section class="section section--light" id="who-we-are" data-animate="fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>TIC was built by people who understand the driver training industry from the inside. We started out operating driving schools, and we still do. Everything we have built since has grown from that base: shared admin, shared systems, shared support, and a group of trusted brands operating across the country.</p>
    <p>The Instructor College is a driver training group. We acquire established driving schools, we operate them as part of our group, and we build practical services for the wider industry. We know what it takes to run a driving school because we do it every day.</p>
  </div>
</section>

{# Our story #}
<section class="section section--alt" id="our-story" data-animate="fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>TIC has grown from operating driving schools into managing a broader group of brands and services. Each step was practical, not theoretical: when we saw something that needed fixing in how a school was run, we built the system, the team, or the process to fix it. Over time, that work became the backbone for the brands we now operate.</p>
    <p>Today the group includes several established driving school brands, our industry service Driving Instructor Car Hire, and a small central team supporting bookings, admin, marketing, instructor onboarding, and compliance across all of them. We are focused on quality driver instruction, strong systems, professional instructors, and long-term industry growth.</p>
  </div>
</section>

